### Summary of key fields:

| Field                   | Purpose                                         | Type           |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- | -------------- |
| `id`                    | Unique room identifier                          | string         |
| `name`                  | Full descriptive room name (displayed to users) | string         |
| `roomType`              | General category/type for filtering/grouping    | string         |
| `description`           | Detailed room description                       | string         |
| `images`                | URLs/paths to room images                       | array\[string] |
| `pricePerNight`         | Cost per night                                  | number         |
| `roomSize`              | Room size                                       | string         |
| `bedInfo`               | Detailed bed setup, total count, types, extras  | object         |
| `maxGuests`             | Maximum guests allowed (adults + children)      | number         |
| `maxAdults`             | Maximum adults                                  | number         |
| `maxChildren`           | Maximum children                                | number         |
| `hasBalcony`            | Balcony availability                            | boolean        |
| `bathroomType`          | Bathroom description                            | string         |
| `isSmokingAllowed`      | Smoking allowed or not                          | boolean        |
| `hasClimateControl`     | Air conditioning / heating available            | boolean        |
| `housekeepingFrequency` | Housekeeping schedule                           | string         |
| `availability`          | Current booking availability                    | boolean        |
| `rating`                | Average customer rating                         | number         |
| `tags`                  | Highlight tags (optional)                       | array\[string] |
| `amenities`             | List of included amenities                      | array\[string] |
| `securityFeatures`      | Security-related features                       | object         |
| `addons`                | Optional extra services or perks                | array\[string] |

